	<tr><td class=bodycopy>

The "Fleet Rome" variant differs from standard Diplomacy in only one detail;
Italy begins the game with a Fleet in Rome instead of an Army.

		<!--BODYCOPY ENDS HERE-->
	</td>
	</tr>
	</table>
	
