	<td class="bodycopy">
		<!--BODYCOPY BEGINS HERE-->

<p>
This variant was created by Richard Sharp and introduced in his book
<u>The Game of Diplomacy</u>.  Sharp felt that starting Italy with a
fleet instead of an army in Rome enhanced play balance.  


		<!--BODYCOPY ENDS HERE-->
	</td>
